title: Psychic Fever from Exile Tribe
text:
Psychic Fever from Exile Tribe (Japanese: サイキック・フィーバー・フロム・エグザイル・トライブ, stylized as PSYCHIC FEVER from EXILE TRIBE) is a boy band formed in 2019. The group is part of the collective Exile Tribe, managed by LDH . They released their debut EP P.C.F in July 2022. 
Originally consisting of nine members, Hanatarou left the group in May 2020, while Sam left the group in April 2022. 


== Members ==


=== Current ===
Tsurugi (剣)
Ryoga Nakanishi (中西椋雅)
Ren Watanabe (渡邉廉)
Jimmy (ジミー)
Kokoro Kohatsu (小波津志)
Ryushin Handa (半田龍臣)
Weesa (イーサ)


=== Former ===
Hanatarou (ハナタロウ)
Sam (サム)
